race.comment: RIGHTEOUS LEGEND (1) is unlucky to still be a maiden hitting the top-five in all seven career outings and strikes a very winnable contest here. Has had two solid trials in preparation for this and can finally break the maiden status against this line-up. LILSISTERDON'TCHA (12) gets 3kg off and strips fitter second-up from the spell. Right in the mix in a race decimated by scratchings. IL FRATELLO (4) is facing the starter for the first time but draws low and has shown some ability at the trials. Any market confidence must be noted. SARAH'S SONNETS (8) draws the inside alley and may be one for the exotics players.
